# Build context = repo root (see Dockerfile header). Docker matches bare
# patterns only at the context ROOT, so `node_modules` / `.next` alone do NOT
# exclude the nested `packages/*/node_modules` + `packages/*/.next` that
# `COPY packages ./packages` would otherwise pull in. Use `**/` so a non-clean
# checkout (stale deps / build output on the host) cannot bloat the context or
# leak old artifacts into the image — the build reinstalls deps and rebuilds
# Next from source inside the image regardless.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.env
.env.local
**/.env.local
dist-widget
.git
